sentences: In the morning informal consultations, parties continued discussion on the carryover of surplus AAUs.

Parties addressed in detail the options in the Secretariat s paper on options for addressing carryover of surplus AAUs to the second and subsequent commitment periods, as well as other party proposals, such as: raising ambition; not carrying over surplus AAUs; capping AAU carryover; and imposing a levy on carryover of AAUs.
